            "title": "SECU_B: Q2 saw margin and EPS gains, robust tech growth, and a new 2030 strategy for 10% EPS CAGR",
            "description": "<div class=\"body-Xl9a4Ubk body-nzzZVyQ3 content-nzzZVyQ3\"><div class=\"symbolsContainer-uFduEtAF logosContainer-diQOvrPB\" data-no-swipe=\"true\"></div><div><span><p class=\"\"><span>Adjusted organic sales grew 3% in Q2, with strong technology and solutions performance, especially in North America. Operating margin and EPS improved, and the 2030 strategy targets 10% annual EPS growth. Liquidity and leverage metrics strengthened.</span></p><p class=\"\"><span>Original document: </span><a class=\"link-zw5jRdec\" href=\"https://www.tradingview.com/accounts/signin?next=https%3A%2F%2Fnews-mediator.tradingview.com%2Fdoc-screener%2Fv1%2Ffiles%2Furn%3Aslides%3Aquartr.com%3A3888941-4c32153cdfad19856583c25852ccd81a\" target=\"_blank\">Securitas AB Class B [SECU_B] Slides Release — Jul. 24 2026</a></p><section class=\"variant-secondary-Gmpzg_mv disclaimer-PlF2Sa64\"><b class=\"heading-wrapper-Gmpzg_mv\"><span class=\"heading-Gmpzg_mv\">Disclaimer</span></b><div class=\"content-Gmpzg_mv link-with-underline-Gmpzg_mv\"><span>This is an AI-generated summary and may contain inaccuracies. Please verify any important information with the original source.</span></div></section></span></div></div>",
